      <title>塔塔钢铁公司利润因一次性成本低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/tata-steel-profit-misses-estimate-on-one-time-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔塔钢铁有限公司第一季度利润未达预期，因为该公司为重组和政治捐款进行了一次性拨备，且收入下降幅度超过预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/tata-steel-profit-misses-estimate-on-one-time-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:27:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北海石油生产商称新税法意味着产量下降速度加快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/north-sea-oil-producers-say-new-tax-rules-mean-faster-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业和分析师表示，英国对石油和天然气公司暴利税制度的变化将加速北海的衰落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/north-sea-oil-producers-say-new-tax-rules-mean-faster-decline</guid>
