    <item>
      <title>美国计划在未来几个季度内保持票据和债券销售稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-plans-to-hold-note-bond-sales-steady-for-several-quarters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部连续第二次维持季度长期债务发行量不变，并维持其指导方针，即预计在“几个季度”内不需要增加票据和债券的发行量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-plans-to-hold-note-bond-sales-steady-for-several-quarters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
